<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-2061] Missing logging for some exceptions</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-2061</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;Since you are using ScheduledThreadPoolExecutor.schedule(), the exception was swallowed by the FutureTask.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You will have to perform a get() method on the ScheduledFuture, and you will get ExecutionException if there was any exception occured in run().&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;</description>
